 Each block contains a hash of the previous block, creating an immutable chain. Applications extend beyond cryptocurrency to supply chain, healthcare records, and voting systems.',\n   280→      tags: JSON.stringify(['technology', 'blockchain', 'crypto']),\n   281→    },\n   282→    {\n   283→      title: 'Thai Cooking Fundamentals',\n   284→      body: 'Thai cuisine balances sweet, sour, salty, spicy, and bitter flavors. Essential ingredients include fish sauce, lime, lemongrass, galangal, Thai basil, and coconut milk. Master dishes like pad thai, green curry, tom yum soup, and mango sticky rice. Fresh herbs and aromatics are key.',\n   285→      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'thai', 'asian']),\n   286→    },\n   287→    {\n   288→      title: 'Astrophotography Guide',\n   289→      body: 'Capturing the night sky requires a DSLR or mirrorless camera, wide-angle lens, sturdy tripod, and remote shutter release. Use manual mode with wide aperture (f/2.8 or lower), high ISO (1600-6400), and long exposure (15-30 seconds). The 500 rule helps avoid star trails.',\n   290→      tags: JSON.stringify(['photography', 'astronomy', 'techniques']),\n   291→    },\n   292→    {\n   293→      title: 'Functional Programming Concepts',\n   294→      body: 'Functional programming treats computation as evaluation of mathematical functions. Core concepts include pure functions, immutability, higher-order functions, function composition, and avoiding side effects. Languages like Haskell, Elixir, and Clojure embrace FP, while JavaScript and Python support FP patterns.',\n   295→      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'functional', 'concepts']),\n   296→    },\n   297→    {\n   298→      title: 'Home Coffee Roasting',\n   299→      body: 'Roasting coffee at home gives you control over flavor profiles. Green beans progress through drying, first crack, development, and optionally second crack. Light roasts preserve origin flavors, medium roasts balance sweetness and body, dark roasts emphasize roast character. Cool beans quickly after roasting.',\n   300→      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'coffee', 'hobby']),\n   301→    },\n   302→    {\n   303→      title: 'Climbing Mount Kilimanjaro',\n   304→      body: 'Kilimanjaro is the highest peak in Africa at 19,341 feet. The Machame route is the most scenic, taking 6-7 days. Acclimatization is crucial to prevent altitude sickness. No technical climbing skills needed, but physical fitness is essential. The summit offers breathtaking views of the African plains.',\n   305→      tags: JSON.stringify(['travel', 'hiking', 'africa']),\n   306→    },\n   307→    {\n   308→      title: 'CSS Grid Layout Mastery',\n   309→      body: 'CSS Grid provides a two-dimensional layout system for the web. Define rows and columns with grid-template, place items with grid-column and grid-row, and use gap for spacing. Grid areas name regions for intuitive placement. Combine with Flexbox for complete layout control.',\n   310→      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'css', 'web']),\n   311→    },\n   312→    {\n   313→      title: 'Fermentation and Pickling',\n   314→      body: 'Fermentation preserves food using beneficial bacteria. Sauerkraut, kimchi, kombucha, and yogurt are popular fermented foods. Basic lacto-fermentation needs only vegetables, salt, and water. Maintain proper salt ratios (2-3%), keep vegetables submerged, and ferment at room temperature for optimal results.',\n   315→      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'fermentation', 'preservation']),\n   316→    },\n   317→  ];\n   318→}\n   319→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_018XL6WPfPMhVktYEhZaQccd","session_id":"dd759fa8-2b0a-48dd-b8de-444b3369a0bd","uuid":"067a9d44-8d3a-4d83-9168-c8e3d8164ca8"}
